                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d573">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.3415/1239a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in Bolivia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Trueblood</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-06-26T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 26, 1931—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>25. Press reports today indicate that Bolivia will break off diplomatic relations
                    with Paraguay unless a denial is made of the recent statement by Paraguayan
                    Chargé in Washington. Please cable at once the situation. The Department and the
                    representatives here of the neutral Governments supposed the situation to be
                    entirely changed now that neutrals’ note has been presented. Breaking off
                    diplomatic relations now when there is possibility for a free and friendly
                    discussion of the whole matter would be a most serious setback in the cause of
                    peace in South America, and the Department desires <pb facs="0848" n="734"
                        xml:id="pg_734"/> you to discuss the matter fully with the Minister for
                    Foreign Affairs and to report the situation fully to it. Department will be glad
                    to have you use your influence in a discreet manner in order to maintain the
                    present situation unchanged.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Castle</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
